snippet.title: Zumba Fitness Core Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Zumba Fitness Core Launch Trailer ! Let's dance ! Join us on Facebook & Twitter http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial & http://twitter.com/gamenewstrailer. Party your abs off with Zumba Fitness Core !

Zumba Fitness Core Launch Trailer. The game is now available on Xbox 360 (Kinect) and Wii ! Subscribe now to get the latest game teasers, gameplay trailers, videogame walkthrough and ingame videos !
